# ConfigLoom [Typescript]

# Package manifest [PackageJson]

The package.json declares Hono as the sole dependency and uses Bun as the runtime.

  [json]
  {
    "name": "loom-hono-hello",
    "private": true,
    "scripts": {
      "start": "bun run src/index.ts"
    },
    "dependencies": {
      "hono": "^4"
    }
  }